&lt;h3&gt;Markdown Basics&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a short reference on how to do formatting in Markdown. This is optional, but may be a helpful reference as you continue on and work with Markdown and RMarkdown.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://sph-r-programming-2022.netlify.app/reference/markdown.html&#34; class=&#34;uri&#34;&gt;https://sph-r-programming-2022.netlify.app/reference/markdown.html&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
