&lt;div id=&#34;swirl-basics&#34; class=&#34;section level3&#34;&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Swirl Basics&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I’m going to highlight another resource for learning basic R concepts: &lt;code&gt;swirl&lt;/code&gt;. This is a software package for R.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;To start it, run the following code in the console in RStudio Cloud:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre class=&#34;r&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;library(swirl)
