&lt;p&gt;You’ll want to take a look at the &lt;code&gt;R Programming&lt;/code&gt; course, especially the following sections:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol style=&#34;list-style-type: decimal&#34;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Basic Building Blocks&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Sequences of Numbers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Vectors&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Missing values&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
</description>
